docli account show-action <id>
docli account (shows the account)

docli domains create <name> <ip>
docli domains show-domain <name>
docli domains delete <name>
docli domains (same as docli list domains)

docli dns <domain> list-records
docli dns <domain> create-record <type> [rec_name] [data] [priority:int] [port:int] [weight:int]
docli dns <domain> show-record <id>
docli dns <domain> update-record <id> <type> [rec_name] [data] [priority:int] [port:int] [weight:int]
docli dns <domain> delete-record <id>

docli droplets list-all-neighbors
docli droplets list-upgrades
docli droplets create <name> <region> <size> <image> [ssh_keys] [--backups] [--ipv6] [--private-networking] [user_data]
docli droplets (same as docli list droplets)

